data.description: Nestled serenely on Lake Como Circle, this captivating five bedrooms with two and one half bath residence is a true testament to timeless elegance and modern sophistication. A harmonious blend of classic charm and contemporary convenience, this approximately 2100 square foot home offers an array of outstanding features that define modern living.  Upon entering the foyer, you're greeted by the rich allure of original hardwood floors that traverse throughout the home, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The living room, adorned with built-in bookshelves, invites moments of relaxation by a wood-burning fireplace, framed by a large front window that fills the room with natural light.  Entertain guests in style within the formal dining room, perfect for hosting gatherings and creating cherished memories. The eat-in kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring 36-inch Quartz countertops, 42-inch cabinets, a flat-top electric stove, a generously proportioned sink, recessed lights, tile flooring, and top-of-the-line Kitchen Aid appliances.   Two of three upstairs bedrooms include ceiling fans, offering a comfortable and tranquil retreat. The basement unveils versatile spaces, including two extra bedrooms or studio/office space, adorned with tile flooring and vinyl trim. An electric fireplace with a wood mantle adds an inviting touch to the basement, while a pantry with shelving, counters, cabinets, and space for a mini fridge enhances convenience. A full bath in the basement provides additional comfort for guests.  Unparalleled storage space is a hallmark of this home, with a substantial storage/utility closet complete with shelving and room to accommodate all your needs. The laundry area is  located in the basement, offering a stackable washer and dryer, counter space, a clothes rack, and a convenient sink, all while housing the water heater and boiler.  For relaxation and leisure, the three-season sunroom beckons with its tile floor, ceiling fan, and TV hookup. Step through its doors onto the back brick patio, where a fire pit and seating wall await your gatherings. A graceful cherry blossom tree provides shade, while meticulously planted arborvitae trees promise future privacy and serenity.  This home has been thoughtfully updated with a new roof, windows, and a remodeled kitchen in 2021, ensuring that every aspect of your lifestyle is considered. Discover the essence of gracious living in the heart of Lake Como Gardens, where this exceptional residence stands as a testament to the finest in luxury and comfort.
